| Input char | Branch | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `i` | Identifier/Keyword branch | `<KEYWORD, int>` |
| `a` | Identifier/Keyword branch | `<IDENTIFIER, a>` |
| `=` | Operator branch | `<OPERATOR, =>` |
